{"tid":1781590,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"梁競徽馬來西亞開個唱賀入行20年 內地網民：什麼時候來内地","createTime":"2019-12-13T09:30:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T02:34:23.000Z","uid":71166,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"64874e02e332eef069c133ec8e75ffae45304f03","tid":1781590,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T09:30:05.000Z","msg":"原名&rdquo;梁烈唯&rdquo;、曾改藝名&rdquo;梁烈維&rdquo;、暱稱&rdquo;唯唯&rdquo;、讀音&rdquo;唯萎&rdquo;、英文名&rdquo;Oscar&rdquo;、曾被網民封為&rdquo;負評王&rdquo;、因於網上大讚華為手機而被稱&rdquo;華唯&rdquo;、新名&rdquo;梁競徽&rdquo;、新暱稱&rdquo;競徽&rdquo;、被網民讀成&rdquo;勁廢&rdquo;、早前被賜勇武新名&rdquo;勁fight&rdquo;、獲封&rdquo;將軍澳清泉&rdquo;、離奇榮升&rdquo;正評王&rdquo;嘅唯萎轉眼間已經入行20年，為隆重其事，佢噚日就喺微博宣佈將於下年2月喺馬來西亞雲頂舉辦首個音樂會並留言話：「入行20年～～～人生中的第一次～希望一切順利～留下一個美好回憶給自己和所以（有）來支持我的朋友❤️2020年2月9號～馬來西亞雲頂星劇場～梁競徽個人首次音樂會😘#梁烈唯超話#梁競徽326超話#演唱會##馬來西亞##雲頂#希望看到您」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/mh0Nrfrbkn5zh3k7IwO25g--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2019-12/f4a29550-1d01-11ea-b7df-ce65020a7ff7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fmh0Nrfrbkn5zh3k7IwO25g--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-12%2Ff4a29550-1d01-11ea-b7df-ce65020a7ff7&h=49ecc6ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/QGzzoQyH5ePCX3OfA59NCw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjkwO2g9NDg3/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2019-12/3f069ec0-1d02-11ea-adff-816b399a7481\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FQGzzoQyH5ePCX3OfA59NCw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjkwO2g9NDg3%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-12%2F3f069ec0-1d02-11ea-adff-816b399a7481&h=29c7b4c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現年40歲嘅梁競徽，1999年參與電影《監獄風雲之少年犯》正式出道，入行多年都係以拍劇為主，雖然都係飾演配角居多，不過當中有唔少經典角色，例如《缺宅男女》關嘉康（關二哥）、《使徒行者》木虱、《飛虎》莊卓源及《鐵探》快活谷等等。至於唱歌方面，佢係冇個人單曲，除咗大型節目或登台表演之外，大家都冇咩機會聽到佢唱歌，究竟佢會喺現場會唱咩歌，大家就真係要拭目以待喇！<br />\n<br />\n一向愛國愛港嘅梁競徽，今次舉行演唱會嘅地方竟然唔係內地，反而選擇喺馬來西亞，唔少內地網民知道消息後都希望有機會睇到佢喺內地演出，紛紛留言話：「支持徽哥，一切順利，也希望内地可以有」、「什麼時候來内地啊，北京歡迎你」、「我都想去啊，來廣州開嗎」、「預祝演出順利哦(&acute;-&omega;-`)有機會考慮下全國巡演哦」及「來内地開演唱會呀，那麼多人喜歡你，應該來呀」等等。"},{"pid":"e2c8966e75513e11ac8414cacc6b40b37faccc76","tid":1781590,"uid":71166,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T09:45:47.000Z","msg":"至於唱歌方面，佢係冇個人單曲，除咗大型節目或登台表演之外，大家都冇咩機會聽到佢唱歌，究竟佢會喺現場會唱咩歌，大家就真係要拭目以待喇！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dd47d610bca39626ad8cd46ad49b96d18e0abd3","tid":1781590,"uid":68463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T09:47:19.000Z","msg":"唱國家?"},{"pid":"cc1ec5d5246c9f79ce41b76522099684af0aca46","tid":1781590,"uid":63124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T09:47:59.000Z","msg":"唱國歌?"},{"pid":"42cf5ec4b69071efb43d15b1a5277521d6a6e15f","tid":1781590,"uid":42487,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T09:49:04.000Z","msg":"「什麼時候來内地啊，北京歡迎你」<br />\n勁FIGHT : 屌你老味...我一直起大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65585fcf6c1b78f5253dc8d7da21de19faf959ce","tid":1781590,"uid":240608,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T09:49:57.000Z","msg":"原來已經40歲"},{"pid":"d4bcd72f715f784bc87c404d66e22e80b98d8eeb","tid":1781590,"uid":71166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"42cf5ec4b69071efb43d15b1a5277521d6a6e15f","tid":1781590,"uid":42487,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T09:49:04.000Z","msg":"「什麼時候來内地啊，北京歡迎你」<br />\n勁FIGHT : 屌你老味...我一直起大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" c